Language Translation Using Azure Translator API

üåê Overview
The Translator API allows automatic translation between multiple languages in real time.

Program:
import requests, json

key = "9VZbnCZ0CCm4xYTKTslmLzPKe588visu9MWrqofpGRSphcgRDhchJQQJ99BKACGhslBXJ3w3AAAYACOGIxSE"
endpoint = "https://centralindia.api.cognitive.microsoft.com/"
path = '/translate?api-version=3.0'
params = '&to=fr'
constructed_url = endpoint + path + params

headers = {
    'Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key': key,
    'Content-type': 'application/json'
}

body = [{'text': 'Hello, how are you?'}]
response = requests.post(constructed_url, headers=headers, json=body)
print(json.dumps(response.json(), indent=2))
